<h2> Definition </h2>

<p>
@KJ{{five^grade}} verbs form the @HI{{zu}}-form by changing the final kana to the @HI{{a}}-row
and adding the suffix @HI{{zu}}. Note that ~@HI{{u}} changes to ~@HI{{wa}}.
</p>

<p>
@KJ{{ichi^grade}} verbs form the @HI{{zu}}-form by dropping the final @HI{{ru}}
and adding the suffix @HI{{zu}}.
</p>

<p>
The two irregular verbs conjugate as shown above.
